%^RESET%^%^BOLD%^%^GREEN%^Prestige Class
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Versatile Arcanist:

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Requirements:
%^RESET%^ Level 20 Sorcerer
%^RESET%^ 20 Base Charisma (before equipment modifiers)

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Class Feats:%^RESET%^
 %^RESET%^L1: greater spell knowledge
 %^RESET%^L4: master of elements
 %^RESET%^L7: master of versatility

Versatile arcanists have a flexible understanding of the weave that only rare sorcerers ever truly obtain. Such mastery of arcana extends not only to the sorcerer's instinctive understanding of magic and magical items, but also grants a command of spells that most normal sorcerers never manage to learn.

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^See also: %^RESET%^feats, skills, spells, cast, prepare, master